userRequest: Build a modern task management dashboard with user authentication, real-time updates, and a mobile-responsive design
finalResponse: Successfully created a comprehensive task management dashboard with authentication, real-time WebSocket updates, responsive design, and comprehensive test coverage. All components are production-ready with proper documentation.

interactions.taskSummary: Analyze user request and create comprehensive project strategy for task management dashboard
interactions.inputReceived: User request: Build a modern task management dashboard with user authentication, real-time updates, and a mobile-responsive design
interactions.outputSummary: Created strategic roadmap: 1) Authentication system 2) Core dashboard components 3) Real-time features 4) Mobile optimization 5) Testing & documentation. Assigned Project Coordinator for tactical execution.

interactions.taskSummary: Coordinate development teams and create detailed project breakdown based on Master Orchestrator's strategy
interactions.inputReceived: Strategic roadmap from Master Orchestrator requiring tactical coordination across development teams
interactions.outputSummary: Created detailed work breakdown: Phase 1 (Backend/Auth), Phase 2 (Frontend/UI), Phase 3 (Real-time features), Phase 4 (Testing). Assigned Full Stack Developer for backend infrastructure.

interactions.taskSummary: Build authentication system and backend API infrastructure for task management
interactions.inputReceived: Requirements: JWT authentication, REST API for tasks, PostgreSQL database, user management endpoints
interactions.outputSummary: Implemented: Next.js API routes, JWT authentication middleware, PostgreSQL database schema, user registration/login endpoints, task CRUD operations, input validation, error handling

interactions.taskSummary: Create responsive dashboard UI components with modern design system
interactions.inputReceived: Design requirements: Mobile-first responsive design, dark/light themes, drag-and-drop tasks, filter/search functionality
interactions.outputSummary: Built: React components with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS styling, responsive grid layouts, task cards with drag-and-drop, search/filter bar, theme toggle, loading states, empty states

interactions.taskSummary: Implement real-time WebSocket functionality for live task updates
interactions.inputReceived: Requirements: Real-time task updates, live collaboration, WebSocket connections, optimistic UI updates
interactions.outputSummary: Implemented: WebSocket server with Socket.io, real-time task synchronization, collaborative editing, connection management, reconnection logic, optimistic updates with rollback

interactions.taskSummary: Create comprehensive test suite covering authentication, API endpoints, and UI components
interactions.inputReceived: Testing scope: Unit tests for API routes, integration tests for auth flow, E2E tests for user workflows, WebSocket testing
interactions.outputSummary: Created: Jest unit tests (85% coverage), Cypress E2E tests, API integration tests, WebSocket connection tests, authentication flow tests, responsive design tests, performance benchmarks

interactions.taskSummary: Generate comprehensive documentation and deployment guide
interactions.inputReceived: Documentation needs: API documentation, user guide, deployment instructions, architecture overview
interactions.outputSummary: Created: README with setup instructions, API documentation with OpenAPI spec, user guide with screenshots, architecture diagrams, deployment guide for Vercel/Docker, troubleshooting section

interactions.taskSummary: Final integration testing and project completion validation
interactions.inputReceived: All deliverables completed, need final validation and integration testing
interactions.outputSummary: Validated: All components integrated successfully, authentication flow working, real-time updates functional, responsive design verified, tests passing, documentation complete. Project ready for deployment.
